{"tid":2090723,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"6月31日 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-07-02T10:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T10:05:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"355b0143371d336d4a0da3a6d37569e18737db64","tid":2090723,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200702/20947730/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947730%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8HQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=11f1f02a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947730%2F&h=1eba7563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200702/20947730/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n6月31日 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200702/large/1593584902_bde3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200702%2Flarge%2F1593584902_bde3.jpg&h=e41330be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n国安法的波板糖=跨境通？<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n喃喃自問。<br />\n<br />\n信口開河<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n第一個即晚舟，無人可憐！<br />\n<br />\n国安法黑幕吹風，預告即拉黎智英與黃之鋒，等同預訂國際頭版。兩位捍衛自由的勇士繫獄，戰狼堅再奸都難以應對外國傳媒。<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n得個桔。一萬蚊和保就業的公帑，亦等於倒咗落坑渠。針對年輕人尤其是眾志被點名那一班細路，雖然腦生蟲的高官「渴望已久」，但戇久係佢嘅事，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n拉緊電箱中的紅線的師傅，驚跨境通是打龍通，問我落唔落疊好。離開唔代表放棄與懦弱，既然後生仔咁講，老餅雖然食塵但打過逆權抗爭的仗，救生艇預留畀高危的後生好了。知命、留守，但獅子銀行唔派息咁衰喎，銀髮無需再疑慮，一於賺藍銀，幫黃圈，救後生，撐蘋果。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}